data.description:
Escape into your private oasis, in the middle of downtown Louisville, at the Mercantile Gallery Lofts, in the East Market Gallery District. Enter the secure luxury building safely, into the private attached garage, with an automatic garage door, to your included parking space and additional storage.  In just a few steps you are in the building, were greeted with a bicycle garage, a courtyard, a beautifully appointed library, workout space, game/entertainment space and a meeting room. Travel up one flight to enter your two-bedroom, two-bathroom loft.  Prepare to be wowed by the ebony-stained concrete floors, floor to ceiling windows, which wash the open concept living, dining and kitchen with natural light.  The custom-built entertainment center houses an 80-inch TV with surround sound, which is perfect for a relaxing evening. The kitchen has a white quartz countertop with a 6-to-8-person matching dining room table. Both bedrooms are spacious and can accommodate a king-size bed.  Both bathrooms have been upgraded with new fixtures. 
The Mercantile Gallery Lofts are just steps from downtown's hottest spots and best amenities, while being far enough away to miss the YUM center traffic, LOL.  This condo offers an unparalleled blend of luxury, location, and lifestyle, set up a showing today.
List of upgrades:
1.	HVAC replaced April 2023
2.	Hot water heater replaced May 2022
3.	Recess lighting.
4.	Decorative columns.
5.	Quartz kitchen countertop with matching dining table.
6.	Ceiling fans in the dining and living room.
7.	New paint throughout condo.
8.	New highboy toilets and new white vanity countertops, in both bathrooms.
9.	New glass front kitchen cabinets.
10.	Custom black drapes and sheers on all windows.
11.	Custom designed entertainment center.
